Sports Project - Basket Ball¶

Dataset cleaning activity¶

1) Team launched year column had improper representation andit was formatted 2) No categorical column was observed 3) Many empty cells were found and since all of them were numeric - is replaced with 0

#converting to actual types for computation - object -> numeric

gameData.PlayedGames = pd.to_numeric(gameData.PlayedGames)
gameData.WonGames = pd.to_numeric(gameData.WonGames)

Overall Best Successful team¶

Best successful team can be calculated with sucess percentage only. Because winning 100 games out of 150 is different from 100 out of 500¶
In [101]:
## Success calculation 

gameData['SuccessPercent'] = (gameData.WonGames / gameData.PlayedGames) * 100

highlySuccessfulTeam = gameData.nlargest(5, ['SuccessPercent'])

highlySuccessfulTeam[['TeamName', 'SuccessPercent']]
